response.original_title: Deep Space 69: Unrated and Fully Unfurled
response.overview: "Deep Space 69: Unrated and Fully Unfurled" chronicles the misadventures of a transport ship in outer space led by Jay and his co-captain Hamilton. A send-up to the many humorless sci-fi films and series over the years that take themselves far too seriously, "Deep Space 69" treads lightly on the topic of space exploration and instead focuses on Jay's incessant exploits with the fairer sex and Hamilton's frustration with these foolish missions. For mature audiences.
